parts.text:
Write a poem based on the topic. Use  {{"type":"tool","path":"file://bgl/tools.bgl.json#module:search-web","title":"Search Web"}}  to gather interesting facts about the topic and incorporate them into the poem.

Each poem must have a title as a markdown heading.
